<p>Reports <code>@Typed</code> annotation usages that violate the following rules:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Only producer methods can have the <code>@Typed</code> annotation</li>
  <li>Bean type must correspond to the types mentioned in the <code>@Typed</code> annotation</li>
</ul>
